hadiths[6]{hadithnumber,text}:
2560,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaein apne makaatibat ke maamle mein unki madad hasil karne ke liye. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko panch auqiya chandi panch saal ke andar panch qiston mein ada karni thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, unhein khud Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karaaney mein dilchaspi ho gaee thi, ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya (ke ye bataao agar main unhein aik hi martaba ( chandi ke ye panch auqiya ( ada kar dun to kya tumharey Malik tumhen mere hath beech dengey ? phir main tumhen aazad kar doongii aur tumhari 'walaa' mere sath qaaim ho jaeygi. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne maalikon ke yahan gain aur unke aagey ye sura rakhii. unhon-ne kaha ke ham ye sura us waqt manzoor kar saktey hain ke 'walaa' hamarey sath rahe. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir mere paas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to khareed kar Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad kar de, 'walaa' to uski hoti hai jo aazad kare. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab farmaya ke kuchh logon ko kya ho gaya hai jo ( maamlaat mein) aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinki koi daleel aur buniyad kitabullah mein nahi hai. isliye jo shakhs koi aisi shart lagaey jiski koi asl (daleel, buniyaad) kitabullah mein na ho to wo shart ghalat hai. Allah Taala ki shart hi zyada haq aur zyada mazbut hai."
2561,"Bareera (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaein apne makaatibat ke maamle mein unki madad hasil karne ke liye. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko panch auqiya chandi panch saal ke andar panch qiston mein ada karni thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, unhein khud Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karaaney mein dilchaspi ho gaee thi, ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya (ke ye bataao agar main unhein aik hi martaba ( chandi ke ye panch auqiya ( ada kar dun to kya tumharey Malik tumhen mere hath beech dengey ? phir main tumhen aazad kar doongii aur tumhari 'walaa' mere sath qaaim ho jaeygi. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne maalikon ke yahan gain aur unke aagey ye sura rakhii. unhon-ne kaha ke ham ye sura us waqt manzoor kar saktey hain ke 'walaa' hamarey sath rahe. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir mere paas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to khareed kar Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad kar de, 'walaa' to uski hoti hai jo aazad kare. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab farmaya ke kuchh logon ko kya ho gaya hai jo ( maamlaat mein) aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinki koi daleel aur buniyad kitabullah mein nahi hai. isliye jo shakhs koi aisi shart lagaey jiski koi asl (daleel, buniyaad) kitabullah mein na ho to wo shart ghalat hai. Allah Taala ki shart hi zyada haq aur zyada mazbut hai."
2562,"Ummul-Momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aik baandi khareed kar usey aazad karna chaha , us baandi ke maalikon ne kaha ke us shart par ham mamla kar saktey hain ke 'walaa' hamarey sath qaaim rahe. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se farmaya ke unki us shart ki wjah se tum na rukoo , 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare."
2563,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) aaein aur kaha ke maine apne maalikon se nau (9) auqiya chandi par makaatibat ka mamla kya hai. har saal aik auqiya mujhey ada karna padega. aap bhi meri madad karein. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke agar tumharey Malik pasand karein to main unhein (ye saari raqam ( aik hi martaba de dun aur phir tumhen aazad kar dun, to main aisa kar sakti hun. lekin tumhari 'walaa' mere sath ho jaeygi. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne maalikon ke paas gain to unhon-ne is sura se inkar kya (waapas aa kar) unhon-ne bataya ke maine aap ki ye sura unke samney rakhi thi lekin wo usey sirf is sura mein qabool karne ko taiyaar hain ke 'walaa' unke sath qaaim rahe. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye suna to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko inform kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to unhein lekar aazad kar de aur unhein 'walaa' ki shart lagaaney de. 'walaa' to bahar-haal usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab kya. Allah ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya, tum mein se kuchh logon ko ye kya ho gaya hai ke) maamlaat mein) aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinki koi asl (daleel, buniyaad) kitabullah mein nahi hai. isliye jo bhi shart aisi ho jiski asl (daleel, buniyaad) kitabullah mein na ho wo baatil hai. chahe aisi so shartein kyon na laga li jaaein. Allah ka faisla hi haq hai aur Allah ki shart hi mazbut hai kuchh logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke wo kehtey hain, aey fulaan! aazad tum karo aur 'walaa' mere sath qaaim rahegii. 'walaa' to sirf usi ke sath qaaim hogi jo aazad kare."
2564,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se madad leney aaiin. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne us se kaha ke agar tumharey Malik ye sura pasand karein ke main (makaatibat ki saari raqam) unhein aik hi martaba ada kar dun aur phir tumhen aazad kar dun to main aisa kar sakti hun. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska zikr apne Malik se kya to unhon-ne kaha ke (hamein is sura mein ye manzoor hai ke) teri 'walaa' hamarey sath hi qaaim rahe. Malik ne bayan kya, unse Yahya ne bayan kya ke Umra ko yaqin tha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to usey khareed kar aazad kar de. 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare."
2565,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke main pahley Utba-bin- abii-Lahab ka ghulam tha. unka jab intiqal hua to unki aulad meri waaris hui. un logon ne mujhey Abdullaah-ibn-abii-Amr ko bech diya aur ibne-abi-Amr ne mujhey aazad kar diya. lekin) bechtey waqt) Utba ke waarison ne 'walaa' ki shart apne liye laga li thi (to kya ye shart sahi hai? ( is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) mere yahan aai thin aur unhon-ne kitabat ka mamla kar liya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey aap khareed kar aazad kar dein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main aisa kar doongii (lekin maalikon se baat cheet ke baad) unhon-ne bataya ke wo mujhey bechney par sirf us shart ke sath razi hain ke 'walaa' unhiin ke paas rahe. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir mujhey uski zarurat bhi nahi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi usey sunaya (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kaha ke) aapko uski itlaa milii. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se malum farmaya, unhon-ne soorat-haal ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Barira ko khareed kar aazad kar de aur maalikon ko jo bhi shart chaahein lagaaney do. chunanche Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khareed kar aazad kar diya. maalikon ne chunkey 'walaa' ki shart rakhi thi isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (sahaaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik majme' se) Khattab farmaya, 'walaa' to usi ke sath hoti hai jo aazad kare. (aur jo aazad na karein) agarche wo so shartein bhi laga lein ('walaa' phir bhi unke sath qaaim nahi ho saktii)."
